Package main.java

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BoardInterface
    Interface that deals with methods regarding the physical board layout.
    MasterInterface
    Interface for controlling the flow of the game--anything dealing with moves and player turns.
    PlayerInterface
    Interface that deals with the players methods.
    RulesInterface
    Interface that deals with the various rules of the game.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AI
    The artificial intelligence working to beat its opponents.
    Board
    Is used to keep track of the positioning of players as well as check whether a new configuration of the board (a player move or a wall placement) is an illegal move.
    Edge
    An extra class in case we needed to utilize a different coordinate system for the walls.
    Player
    Emulates a player on the board by utilizing the same information as a space, but with extra behaviors and attributes.
    Space
    Logical Representation of the spaces of a Board.
    SpaceLinkedList
    Custom Linked-List for creating a graph of SpaceNodes.
    SpaceNode
    Container for the Space objects on the logical board.
    Wall
    Logical Representation of a wall for placement evaluation.
